                <h5 class="card-title" id="itineraryTitle">Day 1</h5>
                <h6>HEAD TO YOUR HOTEL</h6>
                <p class="card-text">Prepare for the best service you’ll find in the area with our pristine exemplary hotels such as Hotel Baker, Courtyard by Marriott or Hilton Garden Inn. There are a total of 11 hotels to choose from in St. Charles.
                  ​</p>
                  <h6>GRAB DINNER</h6>
                <p class="card-text">St. Charles has some of the best restaurants in the area that can accommodate all your cravings.
                    Check out places like E&S Fish Market or Taste of the Himalayas in downtown, or
                    restaurants throughout the town such as Spotted Fox Ale House or St. Charles Place.
                  ​</p>
                  <h6>LISTEN TO LIVE MUSIC</h6>
                <p class="card-text">After you grab some grub, check out the live music scene in town, which is one of the best in all the Chicago suburbs.
                    Some of the hottest places are Club Arcada, The House Pub, and Pollyanna.
                  ​</p>
