                <p class="card-text">St. Charles has the best breakfast 
                    options around. A popular spot in downtown is Brunch Cafe, or
                    checkout other popular breakfast options around town like The Southern Cafe or Syrup. 
                  ​</p>
                  <h6>SHOP</h6>
                <p class="card-text">St. Charles is home to a diverse selection of retail and shopping choices. Upscale department stores like Von Maur call St. Charles home, and local businesses such as Trend & Relic, SG Too, The Pep Line, Jeans & a Cute Top Shop, or one of St. Charles great antique stores that feature a selection of vintage goods and wares. 
                  ​</p>
                  <h6>DINE</h6>
                <p class="card-text">St. Charles has plenty of options to end your day. Visit Rox City Grill, La Za Za Trattoria or The Graceful Ordinary for an upscale dinner along the river and excellent selections of cocktails and drinks. 


                 ​</p>
